Program: Discovery
Title: High-Tech Industry
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwc8
Last Broadcast Date: 16 January 1995
Special report into companies investing in pure research: Hewlett-Packard investigating communications networks: Glaxo investing in neurotransmitters: mathematicians at Hitachi working on single electron circuitry. Presented by Robert Pease.